{
  "name": "RPlog_Little_Storyteller",
  "title": "The Little Storyteller",
  "summary": "Alone in a seaside cliff dwelling as dawn approaches, the young girl Gabi coaxes a dying fire back to life and etches a creation myth into the limestone floor with a shard of fossilized coral. In hushed, ritual cadence she tells the tale of the Sarian people, born from a cataclysm when the angry stars sent a wave of burning fire to punish their ungrateful charges. She recounts how those who heeded the warning signs hid deep within the world of Merganser and survived, emerging changed into a new world, while those who ignored the omens perished. A noise outside, footsteps on the shore, briefly halts her work and quickens her breath. Recognizing the approach of her guardian, the Jedi pilot Leo, she finishes her story, smothers the embers, and creeps off to embrace her krayt dragon companion in the dark.",
